&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://matt.might.net/articles/how-to-apply-and-get-in-to-graduate-school-in-science-mathematics-engineering-or-computer-science/"&gt;如何进入研究生院&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;
